{"tid":982870,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"愛犬爽趴子瑜白滑玉腿　網友發愣：都忘了有條狗了","createTime":"2019-01-15T12:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T14:53:32.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cd53203acc9d0011bf28c40bcf2001a1657b4d28","tid":982870,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/1535960343-5cb12f984119ac887e3b5bbf31d1d924-696x455.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F1535960343-5cb12f984119ac887e3b5bbf31d1d924-696x455.jpg&h=164ad08b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲周子瑜。（圖／資料照）<br />\n韓女團「TWICE」台灣成員周子瑜人氣夯，日前挾著「全球第二美」之勢返台探親，12號帶著大包小包伴手禮回韓工作，昨（14）日她在官方IG秀出返鄉照片，當中抱著愛犬「酷吉」入鏡，網友對女神與寵物意外「撞臉」感到驚奇，也對牠能趴在偶像腿上直呼羨慕，笑言：「酷吉是全世界最幸運的狗！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1547539743-e744aa65035ddb32ab9bfe5e262a5d10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F1547539743-e744aa65035ddb32ab9bfe5e262a5d10.jpg&h=30ac1b61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜昨PO出在家鄉拍攝的美照，並用中文寫下「好久不見」，照片中她緊攬愛犬「酷吉」，時而貼臉時而將牠放在懷中，其中一張子瑜瞇眼自拍，與「酷吉」相似度高達7成，引發熱議，更令網友羨慕的是其實是一段愛犬趴在主人美腿上影片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/1547539748-a3a009bfc1a231db98512bce660c1a0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F1547539748-a3a009bfc1a231db98512bce660c1a0f.jpg&h=b3ef3c28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜與愛犬越來越像。（圖／IG）<br />\n曝光的影片中，子瑜穿著極短熱褲，讓「酷吉」站在她的一雙逆天美腿上，只見「酷吉」被子瑜伸手逗弄顯得相當開心，遂直接將頭趴在主人雙腿，不少網友因此淪陷，大喊，「別跟我搶狗的位子」、「看這腿我忘記有條狗了」、「Gucci是世界上最幸福的狗」，直說「酷吉」被子瑜寵上天了！"},{"pid":"2d713772e8bd54c560725b0044ea90a62272e5bf","tid":982870,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:59:30.000Z","msg":"thx 今晚賓周有著落<br />\n<img src=\"https://pasteboard.co/HWyN1pr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpasteboard.co%2FHWyN1pr.png&h=92c7afef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"482bc31a6348b1dc7f19e24f3c632453b17c0f2f","tid":982870,"uid":76115,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T12:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>thx 今晚賓周有著落<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.pbrd.co/images/HWyN1pr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.pbrd.co%2Fimages%2FHWyN1pr.png&h=d08e1dc1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"61624de0d698a3b56701b8d925ed549763776410","tid":982870,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:01:11.000Z","msg":"玉腿呢?"},{"pid":"b117f9ed1d192fb14255789862ded88458951d1d","tid":982870,"uid":65984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"睇最下幅圖, 隻狗好明顯係人扮"},{"pid":"583b00c0d9acadb73d384df1e810937ab4c4f706","tid":982870,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"腿呢"},{"pid":"6c275fea965ecf8f451f36abce93d529db459342","tid":982870,"uid":165735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:07:57.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"ce2549963bd2a348be798f78d32d6524298a4466","tid":982870,"uid":56782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:16:58.000Z","msg":"ig twicetagram"},{"pid":"ddba977221e653fbc8d95d1af3415084af43c28c","tid":982870,"uid":52073,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:46:34.000Z","msg":"隻狗我黎 成日偷舐小瑜的西"},{"pid":"91fc9f696059fc70cc5017399aac28439beac908","tid":982870,"uid":178658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:47:18.000Z","msg":"玉腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3530ffe48ad6eafd3d13ffa920391ff2ad20d715","tid":982870,"uid":170044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T13:52:11.000Z","msg":"G?"},{"pid":"1aa8a8d290b43bed679dc1abd08514ffc5d41da